Description

Just a simple base hangout app project that shows two of the main functionalities:
How to access participants and how to use the shared data.
To learn more about the Hangouts API please visit https://developers.google.com/+/hangouts/


Installation

  * Edit demo.xml and change <YOUR PATH> to where you plan to upload the files.

  * Upload all the files to <YOUR PATH>

  * Please note that the files need to be publicly accessible.

  * Go to https://code.google.com/apis/console/ and create a new project.

  * Activate the "Google+ Hangouts API" in Services.

  * Go to "Hangouts" and put the full URL to <YOUR PATH>demo.xml in "Gadget URL"

  * Save and you are ready to "Enter a hangout!" :)


